<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Comments: 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
One commenter requested that the Secretary use program announcements to target programs on degrees and certificates
in appropriate areas. Two commenters requested that the Secretary be sensitive to individual student preferences
for attending degree or certificate programs.
